text: Yana Yagodina (born 24 January 1993) is a Kazakhstani volleyball player. She played at the 2013 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2014 FIVB Women's World Championship, 2014 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2018 FIVB Women's World Championship. She played for VC Zhetysu, VC Almaty, and Irtysh Kazkhrome. == References == == Other websites == * https://globalsportsarchive.com/people/volleyball/yana-yagodina/282389/ * Bulgaria V Kazakhstan Fivb Womens World Championship Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani volleyball players
